Invocation Name: weird animal facts
des:
Ask for Weird Animal Facts, and learn bizarre facts about animals from naked mole rats to Orcas. 

Weird Animal Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and a new fact to bring with you to your next party. 

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Weird Animal Facts" or "Alexa, open Weird Animal Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
